.DT
shout
Discworld player help
shout

Name
.SI 5
shout - Shout a message to all the players.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
shout
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Shout is a way of giving a message to all players on the mud.  When you shout
a message, all players are given the message in the following format.
If your name is Shadow and you type 'shout How do I use pf's soul?', all
players would receive the message
.EP

Examples
.SI 5
> shout How do I use pf's soul?
You shout asking: How do I use pf's soul?

Everyone else see's
Lynscar shouts asking: How do I use pf's soul?

Pinkfish shouts: what is your problem?  It is easy to use!

Furball shouts: Give up now.  Pinkfish is the only one who knows how!

Ember shouts: I agree with furball (for once ;)
.EI

See also
.SI 5
soul, say, lsay, tell.
.EI
